elements keyword keyword Element
keyword &keyword.purpose;
&keyword.synopsis.gen; Description
A Keyword is a term describing the content of a document. The keyword applies to the document component that contains it.
Processing expectations
Keywords are rarely displayed to a reader. Usually, they are reserved for searching and retrieval purposes. If they are displayed, they may be displayed either inline or as a displayed block, depending on context.
Unlike SubjectTerms, which should be drawn from a controlled vocabulary, keywords may be chosen freely.
